    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, keeping it garage-stored and detailed regularly. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition, inside and out, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
