    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, maintained with obsessive care and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, gap-free service history from the original dealership. We recently performed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and full fluid flush; the high-performance tires have less than 500 miles of wear. Included with the sale are both original master keys, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle that has been pampered since day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
